reviews.text:
If I had to nail this down in something short and pithy, festive and tasty would be my watchwords. The eggnog is notable and that's a good thing. The hazelnut adds a richness and slight nutty flavor that plays well off the biscuit, which cements the dessert vibe. The vanilla swirl and vanilla pudding add a wall of thick tasty goodness for everything to stick to. Basically, this is a holiday cookie dunked in a glass of eggnog, and it's all very delicious.&#xD;
&#xD;
Nice one!
